 All our websites. 



Legal & General Group is one of the UK's leading financial services companies. To find out more about us, please take a look at the list of all our websites below:



Our Group website


Legal & General Group Plc
This website provides information for customers, shareholders, journalists and those interested in learning more about the Group's performance and results.

                      If you are looking for a job, you can also find information about our latest vacancies on this site.

Company information
Careers
Investors
Media centre
Corporate Social Responsibility


Visit the Legal & General Group Plc website



 



Customer websites


Legal & General customer website
This website provides customers with details of our range of flexible financial products.
Visit the Legal & General customer website


Legal & General Investor Portfolio Service
This website allows customers to monitor and manage the investments they have with Legal & General's Investor Portfolio Service.
Visit the Legal & General Investor Portfolio Service website


Legal & General Workplace Benefits
The place to go if you are an employer, corporate adviser or employee wanting to find out more about our group protection benefits, pensions and savings products.
Visit the Legal & General Workplace Benefits website


Legal & General Business Protection
This website provides employers or employees details about our range of flexible Business Protection products.
Visit the Legal & General Business Protection website


Legal & General Home Finance
This website provides customers with information on our lifetime mortgage products.
Visit the Legal & General Home Finance website



 



Intermediary and Investor websites


Adviser Centre
The website is designed to give Independent Financial Advisers all the information and tools they need to control and develop their business.
Visit the Adviser Centre website


Appointed Representatives Centre
A dedicated website for Appointed Representatives of the
                      Legal & General Network. Find all your literature, compliance and product information here.
Visit the AR Centre website


Bulk Annuities and Longevity Insurance
A dedicated website for Employee Benefit Consultants aimed at providing an overview of our products, team and  publications.
Visit the Bulk Annuities and Longevity Insurance website


Business Opportunities
Whether you're looking to become an Appointed Representative or a Directly Authorised member with exclusive terms, we've got an option to suit you.
Visit the Business Opportunities website


Directly Authorised Centre
A dedicated website for Directly Authorised members of the
                      Legal & General Network. Find all your product and sales information here.
Visit the DA Centre website


Financial Solutions Centre
A dedicated website for our Financial Solutions consultants.
Visit the Financial Solutions Centre


GI Broker Centre
This website provides insurance brokers with information on Legal & General and its general insurance products.
Visit GI Broker Centre website


Legal & General Capital
This website provides information for shareholders, current and future partners (including international investors, councils and developers), journalists and those interested in learning more about our Direct Investment strategy.
Visit the Legal & General Capital website


Legal & General Investments
This website provides a wealth of information about our funds and is designed for wealth managers and investment advisers.
Visit the Legal & General Investments website


Legal & General Investment Management
Our Investment Management website has information on our products for institutional investors.
Visit the Legal & General Investment Management website


Legal & General Workplace Benefits
The place to go if you are an employer, corporate adviser or employee wanting to find out more about our group protection benefits, pensions and savings products.
Visit the Legal & General Workplace Benefits website


Legal & General Investor Portfolio Service (for Intermediaries)
Investor Portfolio Service is our investment platform dedicated to intermediaries.
                      It aims to make your job easier and more rewarding by bringing your clients' investments together in one place.
Visit the Legal & General Intermediary Investor Portfolio Service website


LGV Capital
LGV Capital is a well established provider of private equity in the UK and has professionally managed funds on behalf of external investors since 1988, principally investing through limited partnerships.
Visit the LGV Capital website


Mortgage Club
Find a wide range of exclusive deals and lenders to choose from, plus much more.
                      At Mortgage Club we offer more than just mortgages.
Visit Mortgage Club website


Strategic Partner Centre
This website is designed to give Business Partners all the information and tools that they need to control and develop their business in order to gain a competitive advantage.
Visit the Strategic Partner Centre website



 



Our international websites


Legal & General France
This website provides customers with details of our range of flexible financial products available in France.
Visit Legal & General France


Legal & General Gulf
This website provides information about both our conventional and Takaful (Islamic, Sharia compliant) business operations offered in the Gulf.
Visit Legal & General Gulf


Legal & General Netherlands
This website provides customers with details of our range of flexible financial products available in the Netherlands.
Visit Legal & General Netherlands


Legal & General America
This website provides customers with details of our range of flexible financial products available in the USA.
Visit Legal & General America


Legal & General Investment Management America
Legal & General Investment Management America is a Chicago-based registered investment advisor specializing in active fixed income, liability driven investment (LDI) and index strategies for the US institutional market.

Visit the LGIMA website


Legal & General Investment Management Asia
This website provides information about Legal & General Investment Management (LGIM) in Asia Pacific, with its regional headquarters in Hong Kong. LGIM offers indexing and active fixed income products to institutional investors in the region.
Visit the LGIM Asia website


IndiaFirst Life Insurance
This website provides information about IndiaFirst, Legal & General's joint venture with Bank of Baroda and Andhra Bank.
Visit IndiaFirst Life Insurance


Commercial International Life Insurance Company
This website provides information about CIL, Legal & General's joint venture with CIB Bank in Egypt.
Visit the CIL website








