Accessibility. 



We have built this site to be accessible and usable to as many people as possible.
Whilst we appreciate that it is not possible to create a site that is accessible to absolutely everyone, we have included accessibility checks into our design and build processes to ensure it conforms to the latest accessibility guideline requirements.
Accessibility guideline conformance
We build our content to meet the requirements of Web Content Accessibility Guidelines version 2 (WCAG 2.0) and to meet AA conformance with some exceptions:

PDF document content is often generated by third-party software and may not always meet accessibility standards.
Most video content has captions or a transcript, but currently we aren’t able to provide audio description for all of our videos at this time.

If you have any specific problems with accessing content on this site, please email us using the following address: websitefeedback@landg.com


















