Legal & General - Wikipedia






















 






Legal & General

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Legal & General Group plc)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"L&G" redirects here. For other uses, see L&G (disambiguation).

Legal & General Group plc





Type

Public limited company


Traded as
LSE: LGEN
FTSE 100 Component


