Group Protection.


For 85 years, we've been providing protection to companies who use us to protect their most valuable asset, their employees.
We know that every company is different, so as an employer you can rely on us to quickly and effectively set up and tailor a protection scheme that works for you. Plus, our award winning products and services combined with our passion for treating our customers fairly means you can trust us to deliver financial security to your employees when it really matters.


Our productsThe benefit

Group Life Assurance and Dependants' Pensions
A lump sum benefit that is normally paid tax free up to the lifetime allowance or as a dependants pension, or both when an insured employee dies in service.


Group Income Protection
It can replace lost income due to long term illness or injury. Where appropriate, we can provide early intervention and rehabilitation.


Group Critical Illness Cover
A tax free lump sum benefit for insured employees who suffer from an insured condition, and survive a set time period.


Flexible benefits
We offer a range of flexible protection benefits that can be designed to suit your budget and scheme set up, plus give employees the choice of selecting their own level of cover, within agreed limits.


Ill Health Early Retirement Benefit
Defined benefit pension schemes can face large and unexpected costs when a member retires early because of ill health. Our insurance policy helps businesses de-risk, budget and plan for this unpredictable liability.



Worklife Solutions
Whether you're switching your Group Protection scheme to us or it's your first scheme, it's important to appreciate the collection of benefits that you can take advantage of.
Our Worklife solutions provide a rewarding component to our proposition and enables you to provide your employees with much more.





